videos.description: Auburn's Darrell Williams picks off Stephen Calvert's pass and returns it 26 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Williams runs back pick-6 for Auburn

videos.description: Jordyn Peters comes up with the blocked punt and bats it out of the end zone for a safety to increase Auburn's lead over Liberty to 12-0.
videos.headline: Auburn blocks punt for a safety

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham runs the quarterback keep for an Auburn touchdown at the goal line.
videos.headline: Stidham runs the keeper for TD

videos.description: Jarrett Stidham finds Sal Cannella with a 22-yard touchdown pass to push Auburn's lead over Liberty to 32-0.
videos.headline: Stidham connects with Cannella for TD
